WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.435 --> 00:00:05.639
First setup of PCTV Broadway 2T

00:00:06.687 --> 00:00:10.043
 

00:00:10.244 --> 00:00:12.244
connect Broadway 2T to your internet router

00:00:17.335 --> 00:00:19.335
a wired connection is required for the first setup

00:00:21.206 --> 00:00:26.277
connect the network cable to the LAN port of your router

00:00:28.146 --> 00:00:30.515
and your Broadway 2T

00:00:36.305 --> 00:00:44.513
connect the power supply

00:00:55.676 --> 00:00:57.676
Open http://distan.tv/ in your iPad's Safari browser

00:01:04.970 --> 00:01:06.970
your default password is &amp;lt;&amp;lt;admin&amp;gt;&amp;gt;

00:01:09.608 --> 00:01:11.608
select between different languages

00:01:14.479 --> 00:01:18.468
it is more secure to change your password and TV PIN here

00:01:23.506 --> 00:01:27.143
choose Wi-Fi connection so you will be able to 
 place Broadway 2T anywhere at home without cables

00:01:31.014 --> 00:01:36.871
Broadway 2T will now search for your Wi-Fi network

00:01:39.874 --> 00:01:42.870
enter your Wi-Fi password here once

00:01:43.944 --> 00:01:46.940
and your Wi-Fi connection is set up

00:01:49.534 --> 00:01:55.030
now you can remove the LAN cable and 
 place Broadway 2T at your desired location

00:01:57.342 --> 00:02:00.910
the best place at home is somewhere with good DVB-T reception

00:02:07.370 --> 00:02:17.110
connect the DVB-T antenna to Broadway 2T

00:02:22.069 --> 00:02:29.510
and again, the power supply

00:02:35.167 --> 00:02:39.520
wait, until the green Wi-Fi LED stops flashing

00:02:47.279 --> 00:02:52.990
you can now connect again with http://distan.tv/

00:02:53.636 --> 00:03:02.640
http://distan.tv/ helps you to find Broadway 2T anywhere in your network

00:03:05.281 --> 00:03:11.910
you can now start the automatic channel scan

00:03:13.074 --> 00:03:18.810
it scans completely automatic

00:03:22.234 --> 00:03:24.400
and shows all available channels

00:03:26.605 --> 00:03:31.810
Finished! Broadway 2T is now ready to use...

00:03:50.180 --> 00:03:56.640
take your TV with you, even on an iPhone

00:04:02.000 --> 00:04:04.780
use http://distan.tv/ to find Broadway 2T in your network

00:04:06.347 --> 00:04:13.270
and get access to all your channels

00:04:14.573 --> 00:04:22.820
thanks to h.264 compression take your TV signal 
 with you ... even on the way

00:04:26.937 --> 00:04:37.380
and via internet streaming even while travelling abroad

00:04:41.736 --> 00:04:49.340
Thank you for watching. You can get more information on http://www.pctvsystems.com/

